$ HTML element: details

A `<details>` tag creates a *widget* whose content becomes visible or invisible by the user toggling its visibilty (typically by clicking a triangle).

gh|about-html|/tags/details.html||

{ Closed

  gh|about-html|/tags/img_/details-closed.png||

}
{ Open

  Clicking on the triangle opens the `<details>` content:
  gh|about-html|/tags/img_/details-open.png||

}

sa:

  The CSS `→ development/web/CSS/properties/visibility` property.

  → development/web/HTML/tags
